[We are sorry for the family of the person who died.

There are no clinical signs listed, so it is impossible to hypothesize about the cause of the food-borne situation. It may have been a spoiled food, or an insecticide, or a bacterial toxin. There is not enough information to formulate a supposition. Hopefully more information will be forthcoming. - Mod.TG

